Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.45,0:01:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.15,0:01:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 他是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.95,0:01:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和佐助一样的写轮眼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.65,0:01:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到九尾竟然在这个小鬼的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.35,0:01:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.15,0:01:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会知道九尾的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.75,0:02:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.15,0:02:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我们一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.15,0:02:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鸟的叹息 怒吼吧佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.05,0:02:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙应该就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.25,0:02:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天放学以后陪我修炼手里剑术吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.05,0:02:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你让爸爸教不就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 哥哥的手里剑术更厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我都能看出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.25,0:03:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥为什么总是把我当成麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.35,0:03:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅我吧 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我没空陪你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你每次都说“原谅我 佐助”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后戳戳我的额头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:47.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还说什么“今天”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本就不愿陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.25,0:04:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么哥哥不肯陪我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他有些变了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太喜欢和人交往
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:28.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我这个做父亲的也看不透他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助 你的便当
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你要练习手里剑的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:36.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你回来后 妈妈陪你练吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.35,0:04:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是练习 是修行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.75,0:04:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助 要去学校了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:04:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚才看到鼬了 他真是了不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经是一流的忍者了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七岁以第一名的成绩从忍者学校毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.75,0:05:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十岁就当上了中忍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.55,0:05:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八岁就会使用写轮眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子是我们宇智波一族的骄傲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 佐助几岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.25,0:05:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在的年纪和哥哥毕业时一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.95,0:05:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.15,0:05:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说这些无聊的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.35,0:05:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.95,0:05:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助 你和鼬都是我们宇智波一族的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是木叶的名门
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.45,0:05:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.21,0:05:49.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也会成为像鼬那么厉害的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好学习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和哥哥一样 都是宇智波一族的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会输给哥哥的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,练得太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么 刚刚好像有人在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好暗  现在还不是睡觉的时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.25,0:07:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这究竟是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:07:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔 婶婶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.15,0:08:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动啊 快动 快动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:09:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸和妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.25,0:10:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 你干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干吗 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢的弟弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万花筒写轮眼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的脚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.00,0:11:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要让我看这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.40,0:11:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔 婶婶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸和妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了测试我的器量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,测试器量…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:12:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.70,0:13:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就把大家杀了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.30,0:13:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.80,0:14:35.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有被杀的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.90,0:14:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.30,0:14:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果想杀我 就恨我 憎恨我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后丑陋地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不断地逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拼命苟且偷生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙 可不是泛泛之辈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.58,0:15:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼬 他如果乱跑 会很麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.65,0:15:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不如先砍掉他一条腿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.55,0:15:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.35,0:16:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇智波鼬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.25,0:16:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇智波鼬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.35,0:16:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和佐助一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇智波…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写轮眼啊 而且长得也很像你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.95,0:16:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我…弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说宇智波一族全被杀了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.05,0:16:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是你干的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇智波鼬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:16:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要杀死那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.35,0:17:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在杀掉哥哥之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…绝对不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是佐助提过的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.55,0:17:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要杀掉的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.45,0:17:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如你所说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.35,0:17:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怨恨你 憎恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.65,0:17:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 为了要杀掉你 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.25,0:18:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才活到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.35,0:18:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要…杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.65,0:18:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.75,0:18:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助的绝招 竟然这么轻易就被破了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.15,0:19:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定得想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查克拉覆盖了整个空间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是九尾的查克拉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.45,0:19:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍法.通灵之…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.55,0:19:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 感觉不到查克拉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.25,0:19:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的鲛肌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够削掉查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你使出忍术可就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.05,0:19:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其砍掉脚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:19:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如先砍掉你的手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么使不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.55,0:20:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们对我未免也太不了解了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.35,0:20:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男子汉自来也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.35,0:20:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会被女人所诱惑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反而更擅长用甜言蜜语迷倒她们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.45,0:20:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是绝对不会被女人诱惑的
